overview.en: The Business Alliance Business Chain (BABC for short) is the digital currency equivalent to the digital assets owned by the BABC, which was invested by the British and American Business Council (BABC) to solve business network development issues
overview.zh: 商业联盟商业链（简称BABC）是数字货币，相当于BABC拥有的数字资产，由英国和美国商业理事会（BABC）投资解决商业网络发展问题
